{"FY":[{"def":"A word which expresses blame, dislike, disapprobation, abhorrence, or contempt.","pos":""}],"FYKE":[{"def":"A long bag net distended by hoops, into which fish can pass easily, without being able to return; -- called also fyke net.","pos":""}],"FYLLOT":[{"def":"A rebated cross, formerly used as a secret emblem, and a common ornament.","pos":""},{"def":"The military force of the whole nation, consisting of all men able to bear arms.","pos":""}],"FYTTE":[{"def":"G is the name of the fifth tone of the natural or model scale; -- called also sol by the Italians and French.","pos":""}]}